Education

I'm a Ph.D doctor in Computational physics and my degrees are as follows, M. Sc in Mathematics M. Sc in Applied Physics M.phil in computational Physics Ph. D in computational Physics. I got Ph. D from university of California, san diego California, USA. On the basis of my achievement in degree, my university offered me a job for foundation courses.

Experience

I had served different institutions (national and international) as a subject specialist and head of department. My resume includes the working as, -> Physics lecturer -> Mathematics lecturer & -> Computer lecturer, In different institutions and online classes. Duri g online classes I taught different students, from USA, UK, CANADA & Kuwait. For more details you can contact me through email: adilqayyum@yahoo.com Or WhatsApp at +923365270677. Thanks.

Hobbies

Out of my busy schedule, I'll utilize time for my self. For mind freshness and boosting up my energy I'll do the following activities, Gardening ( I live to produce new sort of roses and other flowers by using different methods, mostly I used stem cutting technique) Poetry writing. Article writing. Books reading. Traveling. Cycling.
